source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_00<tab>Fibubb Gah seeks aid to replenish the Brotherhood's stock of healing salves.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_00<tab>Fibubb Gah aimerait vous demander quelque chose.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_01<tab>Fibubb Gah explains that a true warrior needs to be as concerned with the arts of healing as with the arts of war. Seek out succulents within Zanr'ak and harvest their rejuvenating sap.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_01<tab>Fibubb Gah vous a demandé d'obtenir des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88F20302 /var> sur les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E90230302 /var> de Zanr'ak.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_02<tab>You have obtained a supply of rejuvenating sap. Return to the Ring of Ash and deliver the healing salve to Fibubb Gah.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez réussi à vous procurer les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88F20302 /var> demandé<var 08 ((<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E88F207 /var>)) ((e)) (()) /var>s. Donnez-les à Fibubb Gah, au camp de la Ligue des cendres.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_03<tab>You have delivered the rejuvenating sap to Fibubb Gah. The proud warrior commends your efforts, claiming that a Brotherhood soldier would sooner die in battle than on a sickbed.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_SEQ_03<tab>Fibubb Gah vous a remercié<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> de votre assistance. Continuez de lui venir en aide à l'avenir.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_TODO_00<tab>Obtain vials of rejuvenating sap from succulents in Zanr'ak.
TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the rejuvenating sap to Fibubb Gah.
TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_001<tab>We of the Brotherhood of Ash are proud soldiers all. Yet even the greatest soldier can starve without sustenance, or be crippled by injury.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_001<tab>Nous, membres de la Ligue des cendres, des guerriers puissants nous sommes. De besoins personnels, les guerriers n'ont pas. Mais rester aptes à combattre, ils doivent. Or, chaque jour au combat, ils se blessent.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_002<tab>We bear our battle wounds as badges of honor, but a festering cut can take one's life as surely as the blade of one's foe. A true warrior neglects not the arts of healing.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_002<tab>Les médailles du guerrier, ses plaies sont. Mais s'il y succombe, synonymes de défaites elles deviennent. De savoir guérir ses blessures, il est primordial pour un soldat.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_003<tab>My task for you, honored ally, is simple yet needful: gather from the desert plants of Zanr'ak the rejuvenating sap we use to salve our hurts.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_003<tab>Ô puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> <var 08 E905 ((guerrière)) ((guerrier)) /var><var 1D /var>! De ton aide, nous avons besoin. D'ingrédients pour préparer nos onguents, nous manquons. Quelques <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88F20302 /var>, il nous faudrait. Sur les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E90230302 /var> de Zanr'ak, on peut recueillir ce liquide.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_004<tab>Though our foes make no use of such remedies, they will nevertheless be loath to relinquish them to you. Have a care you do not sustain such injuries that you fail to return!
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_004<tab>S'emparer de ces ressources avant nous, nos ennemis ne doivent pas. De véritables guerriers, les couards de Zanr'ak ne seront jamais. Les récupérer avant eux, pour nous montrer ta valeur tu dois.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_011<tab>Gather the clear sap of the Zanr'ak desert plants, and aid us in keeping our warriors hale.
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_011<tab>Pour préparer nos onguents, des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88F20302 /var>, il nous faut. Sur les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E90230302 /var> de Zanr'ak, on peut recueillir ce liquide. S'emparer de ces ressources avant nous, nos ennemis ne doivent pas.

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_021<tab>Welcome, honored ally. Have you the sap we require?
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_021<tab>Ô puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> <var 08 E905 ((guerrière)) ((guerrier)) /var><var 1D /var>! D'avoir accepté de nous aider, je te remercie. Ce que tu cherchais, as-tu trouvé<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_022<tab>Yes, this will allow our wounded to return to the front lines of battle where a glorious death awaits. No true warrior wishes to wither away on a sickbed...
target: TEXT_BANAMA103_01224_FIBUBBGAH_000_022<tab>Les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88F20302 /var> dont nous avions besoin, ce sont. Soulager nos blessés, nous allons pouvoir. Nos re<var 16 /var>mer<var 16 /var>cie<var 16 /var>ments, tu mérites<var 1D /var>!
